title: Huma Abedin Cut FBI Deal, Kept Clinton E-Mails in ‘Life Insurance’ Folder?
subtitle: Rumors claimed that Huma Abedin retained deleted e-mails belonging to Hillary Clinton in a folder called "life insurance," and cut a deal with the FBI for them.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: Huma Abedin retained deleted e-mails of Hillary Clinton's in a folder marked "life insurance" and cut a deal with the FBI.
